title: Provides that the power of eminent domain shall only be exercised for economic development purposes when the area for economic development is a blighted area
summary: Provides that the power of eminent domain shall only be exercised for economic development purposes when the area for economic development is a blighted area.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the eminent domain procedure law, in relation to the exercise of the power of eminent domain to develop blighted areas of the state
